4:
Thanks for helping me find Fluffy! I'm
really happy I met you!
7:
Don't mention it! Just be careful not
to lose Fluffy again, okay?
14:
Lady Yuna! May I have a word with
you!
19:
Huh? What are you three doing
here?!
23:
A concern over your lack of
recreation has brought us to you.
27:
Lack of recreation? What do you
mean! I'm having a blast taking on
different jobs and helping people!
30:
Besides, I'm finding time to take it
easy every now and then, too. So
don't worry—
36: That is NOT what I meant!
42:
WE'RE the ones who aren't getting
enough playtime, Yuna! Playtime
with YOU!
56:
Heh-heh... We're going to have a
great day together.
61:
...Okay, sure! Let's go have a great
time!
66: Very well. Let us be off!
75:
You'll vanish the second we take our
eyes off you, so today's plan is going
to be on rails!
83:
How trivial... I will guide my blade not
with my eyes, but my heart! Hiyaaah!
98:
Urk! Th-this cannot be! I insist on a
rematch!
105:
Oh, so this is the casino! It's my first
time seeing it!
109:
It is? Well, let me teach you a thing
or two about how to win big.
114:
Yes, please! I'll leave it to you,
Nimbus!
123:
Yay, I won again! This is so much
fun! Right, Nimbus?
135: Ah... This vacation is the best...
143:
Thanks, Pythica... For inviting me
along today.
146:
I mean, the way you dragged me
along was super brash. But I'm
always involving myself in others'
affairs, too, right?
149:
So for somebody to finally do it back
to me? I'm super lucky to have that
experience!
156:
But you know? Your way of involving
yourself with others is still unique.
159:
I guess it's just because of who you
are as a person? Like, in the way you
just can't ignore a person in need.
163: Huh? What are you getting at?
166:
But... I guess I do have my own way
of doing things, huh? And it's not like
I could change that now, even if I
wanted to!
168:
But that doesn't mean I don't want
to keep improving myself.
172:
Yeah! I wish I could do so much
more than I can right now... I want to
catch up with everyone else!
181:
Now then, what should we do next? I
think we should try doing anything
and everything we can!
185:
Maybe we could go souvenir
shopping! There are tons of stores
here!
190:
Ah, right! I've gotta buy souvenirs for
people back in Starview!
193:
Who did I promise souvenirs to
again? ...Right, Walter and Evan...
196:
And then there's Rico, Nochel,
Conner, Millet... Also Grieg, Marnie,
Jester, uh... Oh, and my teacher, too!
200:
Ahaha, that sounds great, Yuna!
You've certainly got your work cut
out for you!
212:
Huh?! Your teacher's in Starview?!
Who is it? Someone I know, maybe?!
215:
Oh, did I never tell you who it was?
I'm sure you'll get a chance to meet
when we get back.
219:
Probably off drinking in some cool
spot somewhere... And probably
wearing that yukata, too!
226:
Anyway, we should hurry up and go
shopping now!
236:
Just wait a little longer, Teach! I've
got a whole treasure trove of
vacation stories to share with you!
